 />\n<br />\n公屋可以租出去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賣斷咗嘅公屋應該計入私人市場？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 私人市場<br />\n不過百幾呎公屋, 租7500? 得唔得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然百零呎 但假假地都係間屋<br />\nD劏房唔夠200呎都租緊7-8000"},{"pid":"ca884b380bc05bb3339c6bab97b4a71e1c90fb51","tid":17784,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"首置稅務優惠用係間公屋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58b3b81b9313b29c3ef71d3af55507495b6cca8","tid":17784,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"信蘋果日日唱淡既下場就係租樓日日賺！"},{"pid":"ff9c58489640d5bdf4de78c3a6f6d2741cd4e947","tid":17784,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"> 買家為首置客，計劃買入單位投資收租，預計收租約7,500元，租金回報率大約4.7厘。 </span><br />\n<br />\n公屋可以租出去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賣斷咗嘅公屋應該計入私人市場？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 私人市場<br />\n不過百幾呎公屋, 租7500? 得唔得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然百零呎 但假假地都係間屋<br />\nD劏房唔夠200呎都租緊7-8000</blockquote><br />\n鳳德地頭算方便"}]}